Package: GRAFit
Type: Package
Title: An Automatic Structural Decomposition Pipeline for HST imaging data (GRAFit)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hosein Hashemizadeh
Maintainer: Hosein Hashemizadeh <abdol.hashemi@gmail.com>
Description: GRAFit is an automatic pipeline for galaxy structural decomposition, also known as bulge-disk decomposition. 
             GRAFit is oroginally designed for the Hubble Space Telescope (HST) high-resolution imaging data, however, 
             it can be used widely on any astronomical images containing a galaxy. 
License: LGPL-3+
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    ProFit,
    ProFound,
    foreach,
    doParallel,
    celestial,
    magicaxis,
    LaplacesDemon,
    FITSio
Imports: astro,
    doParallel,
    knitr,
    RColorBrewer,
    Cairo,
    doSNOW,
    data.table
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
